    <item>
      <title>Re: Message Stats Error</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/ezpm/forum/general/message_stats_error/re_message_stats_error</link>
      <description>Hi Max,&#13;
&#13;
Thanks for reporting this bug. eZ Publish 4 needs more changes in my extension than I thought. You can solove this problem editing file autoload/ezp_extension.php in your eZ Publish root directory and adding the following at the end of array:&#13;
&lt;code&gt;&#13;
               'eZPm'                      =&gt; 'extension/ezpm/modules/pm/classes/ezpm.php',&#13;
&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
This weekend I will commit new version of eZPm extension, so some other bugs will be fixed.&#13;
&#13;
Cheers</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Bartek Modzelewski)</author>
      <guid>http://projects.ez.no/ezpm/forum/general/message_stats_error/re_message_stats_error</guid>
